- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with speech translation, which involves processing audio signals.
- cs.LG (Learning) is a possible category as the paper explores the effectiveness of transfer learning in SLT.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with neural models and machine translation.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with speech translation, which is a form of multimedia processing.
